org.osate.xtext.aadl2.errormodel.errorModel

Interface ErrorDetection

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AObject, Element, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.core.runtime.IAdaptable, NamedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ErrorDetectionImpl

    public interface ErrorDetection
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NamedElement
    A representation of the model object 'Error Detection'.

    The following features are supported:

    • State
    • Type Token Constraint
    • All
    • Condition
    • Internal Detection Port
    • Detection Reporting Port
    • Error Code

    See Also:
    ErrorModelPackage.getErrorDetection()
